#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Access the rates from the same menu to see how price rules apply during the "
"year."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.homepage
msgid ""
"Accommodation were exactly what we needed for a family moment.<br/>Many "
"thanks agan."
msgstr ""
"家族で過ごすのにぴったりの宿泊先でした。<br/>本当にありがとうございました。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add here as many of them as needed."
msgstr "必要なだけ、ここに追加してください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust the number of stars, leave a comment and send it!"
msgstr "星の数をお選びいただき、コメントをご記入のうえ、送信してください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the rental dates, click the book button and then proceed to checkout."
msgstr ""
"滞在日を選択し、「予約」ボタンをクリックしてから、お支払い手続きに進んでくだ"
"さい。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust your prices along the year"
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjusting your offers in consequence"
msgstr "それに応じてオファーを調整します"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Again, the <strong>Holiday House App </strong>helps you manage the end of "
"the stay!"
msgstr ""
"ここでも、<strong>ホリデーハウスアプリ</strong>は滞在の最後まで管理をサポート"
"します!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.custom_product_name
msgid "All Houses"
msgstr "ハウス一覧"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively to individual resource blocking slots described earlier, you "
"can select a resource this leave applies to."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, which is more suitable if the "
"booking is not during the visualized date range and update the booking date "
"range."
msgstr ""
"または、リストビューに切り替えてください。表示されている日付範囲外の予約の場"
"合は、リストビューの方が適しています。併せて予約の日付範囲を更新してくださ"
"い。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type in the search bar and select the appropriate filter."
msgstr "または、検索バーに入力して適切なフィルタを選択してください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can create a slot as placeholder from the planning "
"directly:"
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.homepage
msgid ""
"Amazing stay at the heart of a pine tree forest. Resourcing and peaceful. "
"<br/>Lovely furnished with all the necessary, even including games such as "
"Mölkky. <br/>I can only recommend!"
msgstr ""
"松林の中心での素晴らしい滞在。心が癒され、穏やかな時間を過ごせました。<br/>必"
"要なものがすべて揃った素敵な内装で、モルックのようなゲームまで楽しめます。"
"<br/>心からおすすめします！"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_12
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_13
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_14
msgid "An address must be specified for a map to be embedded"
msgstr "マップを埋め込むにはアドレスを特定する必要があります"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Anyone can create a portal account on your database.<br/>\n"
"Open your website home page in a private tab to do so."
msgstr ""
"誰でもあなたのデータベース上でポータルアカウントを作成できます。<br/>\n"
"ウェブサイトのホームページをプライベートタブで開いてください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Assign them a resource, which helps you keeping track."
msgstr "リソースを割り当ててください。これにより進捗管理が容易になります。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time from the guest order, use the Send message capability in the "
"chatter to exchange with your guest."
msgstr ""
"ゲストのオーダ画面からいつでも、チャターの「メッセージを送信」機能を使ってゲ"
"ストとやり取りできます。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time you can adjust the city tax count delivered by re-opening the "
"city tax widget clicking the City Tax button on the guest order."
msgstr ""
"いつでも、ゲストのオーダ画面にある「宿泊税」ボタンをクリックして宿泊税ウィ"
"ジェットを再度開くことで、宿泊税の数を調整できます。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model:product.template,name:holiday_house.product_template_14
msgid "Beach House"
msgstr "ビーチハウス"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Blocking resources"
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Booking a house"
msgstr "ハウスを予約"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products, sale orders and more."
msgstr ""
"このモジュールのデモデータをアップロードすることで、データベースにいくつかの"
"プロダクト、販売オーダなどが追加されました。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your customer for the resulting amount and you're all set!"
msgstr "最終的な金額を顧客に請求すれば、準備完了です!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your guests"
msgstr "ゲストに料金を請求する"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Check and adjust if needed the number of guest who stayed in each room. Then "
"confirm the number of city tax to be charged, which updated the delivered "
"city tax count."
msgstr ""
"各部屋に滞在した宿泊者数を確認し、必要に応じて調整します。その後、請求すべき"
"宿泊税の数を確定すると、実際に発生した宿泊税の件数が更新されます。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests in"
msgstr "ゲストをチェックイン"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests out"
msgstr "ゲストをチェックアウト"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check the invoice data and confirm it."
msgstr "請求書のデータを確認して確定してください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"City Taxes are to be billed to spent nights in practice and not in theory "
"and are counted as the sum of nights each guest stayed."
msgstr ""
"宿泊税は、理論上ではなく実際に宿泊した宿泊日数に対して請求され、各宿泊者の宿"
"泊日数の合計としてカウントされます。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click one of the house to book."
msgstr "ハウスをクリックしてご予約ください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Check in button to confirm they are now staying at your place!"
msgstr ""
"「チェックイン」ボタンをクリックして、滞在を開始したことを確認しましょう!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Check out button to capture they return you the keys."
msgstr ""
"鍵の返却を記録するには、「チェックアウト」ボタンをクリックしてください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Create Order to open the order form."
msgstr "オーダフォームを開くには、「オーダ作成」ボタンをクリックしてください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Invoice button with a full invoice."
msgstr "請求書の全内容を表示するには、「請求」ボタンをクリックしてください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Pay with demo button, and then Pay button to mimic the payment."
msgstr ""
"デモで支払うには、「デモで支払」ボタンをクリックし、その後「支払」ボタンをク"
"リックしてください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the tail of the corresponding booking and drag it to the requested "
"date."
msgstr "該当する予約の末尾をクリックし、希望の日付までドラッグしてください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new leave selecting the appropriate working schedule, the one from "
"your stay resources."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new leave the same way as previously, but this time specify the "
"resource this applies to."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Created offers are assigned no company nor branch (default behavior).<br/>As "
"a result, they are available from all companies and branches, as well as all "
"websites from those."
msgstr ""
"作成されたオファーには、会社も支店も割り当てられません(デフォルト動作)。<br/>"
"その結果、すべての会社と支店、およびそれらのすべてのウェブサイトから利用可能"
"となります。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Define start and end date time and save your leave."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Odooについて更に知りましょう。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"本パッケージの基本を理解し、Odooで提供している全てについて詳しく知ることで、"
"ユーザ経験を向上させることができます。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Don't forget to save your setting changes."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"During an available period, click, drag and drop on a house line to create a "
"slot."
msgstr ""
"空いている時間帯に、ハウスラインをクリック、ドラッグ、ドロップしてスロットを"
"作成します。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
