"海岸線の上に浮かぶように建つこのビーチハウスは、海と空を一望する壮大な眺めを"
"お楽しみいただけます。自然のありのままの美しさとミニマルな快適さが調和し、自"
"然の力強さと近さを全身で感じられる、思い出に残る隠れ家での滞在をお約束しま"
"す。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The strength of Odoo is to separate the accounting and many other aspects "
"which are company dependent!"
msgstr ""
"Odooの強みは、会計をはじめとした多くの会社依存の要素を明確に分離できることで"
"す!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Then set the days during which you want to prevent check in and check out to "
"take place, ex. All days but Saturday"
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"これらは全て、現在ご契約中のサブスクリプションで無料でご利用いただけます!🙃"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"They as well share the same pricing, defined at the stay offer level, which "
"has its pros and cons."
msgstr ""
"宿泊プランのレベルで定義された同じ料金設定も共有されており、それにはメリット"
"とデメリットがあります。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "They were happy about their stay, let's ask them to leave a review."
msgstr ""
"ご満足いただけたとのことで、大変うれしく思います。よろしければ、ご感想をお聞"
"かせください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This blocks simulataneously all resources related to this working schedule "
"during the prescribed period."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This setup is relevant in case of place specific offers or when pricing "
"varies between places."
msgstr ""
"この設定は、地域限定のプランがある場合や、場所によって価格が異なる場合に適用"
"されます。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time, simply leave a note about the why this is booked and save the "
"slot."
msgstr "今回は、この予約の理由をメモに残して、スロットを保存するだけです。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Trace guest attendance"
msgstr "ゲストの利用履歴を記録する"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:holiday_house.product_template_13
msgid ""
"Tucked among tall pine trees, this A-frame cabin is designed for rest, "
"reconnection, and remote living. With natural light, open space, and all the "
"essentials for comfort, it’s a perfect escape for those looking to slow down "
"and recharge in a serene forest setting."
msgstr ""
"背の高い松の木々に囲まれたこの A フレームキャビンは、休息・再接続・リモート滞"
"在のためにデザインされています。自然光が差し込む開放的な空間と必要な快適設備"
"がそろい、静かな森の中でゆっくりと過ごし、心をリセットしたいゲストにとって理"
"想的な隠れ家です。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Two options are now available to you with multiple companies and branches:"
msgstr "複数の会社や支店がある場合、以下の2つの選択肢が利用可能です："

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Type in the customer name in the Schedule search bar filtering by Customer."
msgstr "スケジュールの検索バーに顧客名を入力し、「顧客」で絞り込みましょう。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome your guests as well from the Holiday<strong> House App</strong>."
msgstr "ホリデー<strong>ハウスアプリ</strong>からもゲストをお迎えしましょう。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When creating an offer, assign them a company or a branch.<br/>As a result, "
"they are available only for the selected company or branch, and will be "
"available only from its website."
msgstr ""
"プランを作成する際には、会社または支店を割り当ててください。<br/>これにより、"
"選択した会社または支店でのみ利用可能となり、そのウェブサイトからのみアクセス"
"可能となります。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the create slot for this resource, no overlapping booking slot would be "
"created.<br/>Care about the start and end time or this blockage to make to "
"re-open when suited."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "Odooのセットアップについてご相談、またはそれ以上をご希望ですか?"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are repairing a house or simply welcoming family and don't want guests "
"to book it?<br/>Alternatively, you are closing for a week during an inter "
"season break?<br/>Let's have this reflected in your schedule!"
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"メインダッシュボードからOdooデータベースにインストールされている全てのアプリ"
"にアクセスできます。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well select your company and in the Branches tab define branches."
msgstr "会社を選択することもでき、[支店]タブで支店を定義できます。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ユースケースのデモは終了です! ビジネスニーズに応じて、Odooのセットアップを適"
"応させる方法は他にも沢山あります。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You could customize this section to add the identity document picture or "
"extra fields at your convenience with studio. Just be careful, such "
"customizations can quickly become messy."
msgstr ""
"このセクションは、スタジオを使えば身分証明書の画像や追加項目など、自由にカス"
"タマイズできます。ただし、こうしたカスタマイズは複雑になりやすいので注意して"
"ください。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade your package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"デモデータのインポートはまだ可能です。アプリ&gt; インダストリー&gt; パッケー"
"ジをアップグレードに進み、該当するボックスにチェックを入れてください"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You have a future guest on the line willing to book a house?"
msgstr "今、家を予約したいという将来のゲストから電話が来ていますか?"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You holiday house is online and future guests found it!"
msgstr "あなたのバケーションハウスが公開され、将来のゲストの目に止まりました!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You just installed the Odoo for Holiday House package. By doing so, we "
#| "have installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your bar efficiently."
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Holiday House package. By doing so, we have "
"installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your business efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Odooホリデーハウスパッケージをインストールしました。これにより、ゲストハウス"
"を効率的に運営するために必要なアプリ群がインストールされました。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may be running multiple places at the same time and most likely be "
"willing to run them all from the same database.<b/>We got you covered with "
"this using multiple companies or branches!"
msgstr ""
"複数の施設を同時に運営しており、それらをすべて同じデータベースで管理したいと"
"お考えかもしれません。<b/>その点もご安心ください。Odoo では、複数の会社や支社"
"機能を使って対応できます!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may want to uplift your margin during high season and be attractive "
"during low one playing on price.<br/>To do so, let's define price rules."
msgstr ""

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You might have tested this package with or without demo data."
msgstr ""
"このパッケージを、デモデータの有無にかかわらずテストされたかもしれません。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You noticed that the Identity Check highlights whether you captured all the "
"necessary information for a guest?"
msgstr ""
"身分証明チェックが、ゲストに必要な情報をすべて取得できているかどうかを示して"
"くれることに気づきましたか?"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"このパッケージをOdooで活用すると、さまざまなフローを簡単に実行できます。 全体"
"の流れを把握するために、以下の操作を試してみて下さい。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You welcome your first guests, awesome!"
msgstr "初めてのゲストをお迎えしました。すばらしい!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You're now waiting for your guest to arrive."
msgstr "あとはゲストの到着を待つだけです。"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.homepage
msgid ""
"Your Dynamic Snippet will be displayed here... This message is displayed "
"because you did not provide both a filter and a template to use.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"ダイナミックスニペットはここに表示されます...使用するフィルタとテンプレートの"
